In this frame, a Resource_controller is judged by a Judge (who is usually implicit) according to how freely they allow the Recipient access to their Resource. The Resource_controller may exhibit this attitude with an Expressor. John is mean with money.

generous.a, hoard.v, lavish.a, lavish.v, mean.a, miserliness.n, miserly.a, miser.n, niggardliness.n, niggardly.a, stingy.a, ungenerous.a
